pkghelpers: pkghelpers (Helper script for making packages)
pkghelpers: This script installs several helper functions for making
pkghelpers: Slackware packages:
pkghelpers: - pkghelpers_env: sets various environment variables
pkghelpers: - pkghelpers_fixup: strips binaries and other standard fixes
pkghelpers: - pkghelpers_makepkg: checks the package 'sanity' and makes
pkghelpers:    makes the package.
